product_description: The HEAD Ti. Conquest Tennis Racquet is the perfect choice for beginners and recreational players looking for a lightweight, powerful, and easy-to-handle racquet from one of the most trusted brands in tennis. Its 108 sq in oversize head provides a large sweet spot that makes hitting clean shots easier, even for players still building consistency. Pre-strung and ready to go straight out of the box, the HEAD Ti. Conquest delivers reliable power, stability, and comfort—making it one of the best beginner tennis racquets for adults, casual players, and anyone returning to the sport. Whether you're practicing at the park, taking lessons, or playing recreational matches, this racquet is engineered to make the game more enjoyable from day one.
